{
  "stem": "7160.1",
  "chunk_idx": 16,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In the same time, about 20 people, they grab me from the neck, from the arms, from the legs.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, want to hold something.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They don't know how to swim.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I start punching left and right to liberate myself.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So finally, about 3/4 [LAUGHS] dead, I arrived to the other side of the river, where the other Nazis was waiting over there.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then you see thousands of people flying in the-- on top in the river-- the corpses-- people who got drowned, who got shot, the one that cannot-- they were afraid to go in the water.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I don't know what happened to those people-- to the-- either they picked them out or they left them over.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So then they put us together and tell us, keep marching.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From the bridge.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They had the machine guns on top.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and we-- we had to go across through the river.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The bridge was not a very big thing, you know?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they didn't want also the civilian to see very much.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, they tried to hide as much as they can.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so from there, we-- we start walking again, and walking.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "On the river, what I did is, I soaked my clothes good before I left there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That way, I figure-- but I think I can-- when I get thirsty, I can suck the-- the jacket or anything, and have something to drink-- something-- that.",
      "word_count": 28
    }
  ],
